        <productionVolumeComment xml:lang="en">In Switzerland, 90% of the sewage sludge is disposed through municipal incineration and 10% in landfarming. Therefore, the PV for each disposal method is calculated based on the respective percentage of the total PV of sewage sludge generated during the wastewater treatment process
